<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Lumudan</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-24 10:34:28</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Best way to take Gorlik is to go in from the entrance with a goblin on each side. You basically make three rights and youl be in a "corner room". The third right is a little confusing but you should pass a table/chairs in the hall and the hall slopes downward. Once your in the corner room, just sit and wait. Lotsa wanderers here so keep them cleared out. Gorelik will wander by and youll hear him casting when he spawns. <BR>
<BR>
Spawn is 2 hours, and hes dropped the staff 3 out of 4 times for me.<BR>
<BR>
He is level 41 and will have a pet. He cast dispel, root, and togor's often and can double for 90-100.</font></td></tr></table>
