<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Soop</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-09 15:05:19</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am now a lvl 32 ogre warrior with some really good stats, and str being a natural for ogres, I hit hard anyway... but with this.... <BR>
<BR>
Lucked into seeing an auction in Oasis for a mith staff for 300pp.  Had just seen the staff on Ebay and thought the stats rocked.  I got it... for the 300pp. =)<BR>
<BR>
Had been using the axe but after using the staff I notice one very important thing, when grouped with an ENC, their augment is canceled by the shortlived proc of the axe.  Not usint the staff ).  and when i do get a FBSS... hehe.<BR>
<BR>
As for 2hb. got the staff at lvl 25 and took till lvl 29 to max it... keep in mind though that could not use it full time when it didnt work.  only when in a good group could i practice, till it got up to at least 80 or so.  Now is maxed and have to make myself practice the axe each level ).<BR>
<BR>
Get one.  the things are relativly cheap due to the 2hb skill level problems.  Is a GREAT warrior weapon.<BR>
<BR>
And yes, I too am asked if i am a shaman, even though i look like a blueberry the size of Rhode Island and am walking very slowly, hehe.<BR>
<BR>
Soop, Brell server<BR>
the good ogre =)<BR>
