<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yes, yes. This is a great weapon. Everyone has already put in a good word about it, so I have no real reason to repeat what is already known. I've been using this weapon since level 31, and I'm quite use to its power. Now, I'm level 41 and am hungry for more power. I'm curious if anyone knows what weapon I should upgrade to after this powerful (but not too stylish) weapon. <BR>
Now this is a comment page for the Mithril Staff, so let me add my little comments. Highest non-critical hit thus far is 109, highest critical is 171, and highest crippling is 269. I love the weapon, and so should you.</font></td></tr></table>
